k" target="_blank">week</a> by the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_International" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_International" target="_blank">news</a> of hundreds more <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa" target="_blank">North Africans</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">dying</a> in the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mediterranean_Sea" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mediterranean_Sea" target="_blank">Mediterranean</a> while attempting to escape <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/War" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/War" target="_blank">war</a> and hardship This is an issue that the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Government" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Government" target="_blank">Scottish Government</a> has raised with the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom_coalition_government_%282010%E2%80%93present%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom_coalition_government_%282010%E2%80%93present%29" target="_blank">UK government</a> since last <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" target="_blank">year</a> when the search and rescue <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missionary" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missionary" target="_blank">mission</a> Mare Nostrum was first withdrawn  and as a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government" target="_blank">government</a> we will continue to urge <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europe" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europe" target="_blank">European nations</a> to do more to help the world's refugeesEarlier <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News" target="_blank">this week</a> the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_National_Pa